/// recommendation : "<p>\r\n   <span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: #920b0b;\">\r\n   <b>Insights for your consideration:</b>\r\n   </span>\r\n</p>\r\n<ul type=\"disc\" style=\"margin: 5px 0;\">\r\n   <li class=\"MsoListParagraph\">\r\n      <p><b>\r\n         <span style=\"font-size: 13px;color: black;\">Market Performance: </span>\r\n         </b>\r\n      </p>\r\n      <p>\r\n         <img src=\"https://docs.investwellonline.com/cloud_investwell_images/logo/TemplateImages/alphacapital^image003.png\" style=\"width:270px\" />\r\n      </p>\r\n   </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul type=\"disc\" style=\"margin: 5px 0;\">\r\n   <li class=\"MsoListParagraph\">\r\n      <p style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">\r\n         <b>\r\n         <span style=\"font-size: 13px;color: black;\">Market Trends:</span> \r\n         </b>\r\n      </p>\r\n      <ul type=\"circle\">\r\n         <li class=\"MsoListParagraph\">\r\n            <span style=\"font-size: 13px;color: black;\">January witnessed heightened volatility across Indian and global markets, including equities and commodities.</span>\r\n         </li>\r\n         <li class=\"MsoListParagraph\">\r\n            <span style=\"font-size: 13px;color: black;\">Indian equities were impacted primarily due to geopolitical uncertainties.</span>\r\n         </li>\r\n         <li class=\"MsoListParagraph\">\r\n            <span style=\"font-size: 13px;color: black;\">Commodity markets remained highly volatile during the month. Most precious metals touched new highs before witnessing sharp drawdowns.</span>\r\n         </li>\r\n      </ul>\r\n   </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul type=\"disc\" style=\"margin: 5px 0;\">\r\n   <li class=\"MsoListParagraph\">\r\n      <p style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">\r\n         <b>\r\n         <span style=\"font-size: 13px;color: black;\">Investor Flows:</span> \r\n         </b>\r\n      </p>\r\n      <ul type=\"circle\">\r\n         <li class=\"MsoListParagraph\">\r\n            <span style=\"font-size: 13px;color: black;\">Foreign Institutional Investors remained net sellers during January.</span>\r\n         </li>\r\n         <li class=\"MsoListParagraph\">\r\n            <span style=\"font-size: 13px;color: black;\">Domestic Institutional Investors (DIIs) provided partial support, cushioning the downside to some extent.</span>\r\n         </li>\r\n      </ul>\r\n   </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul type=\"disc\" style=\"margin: 5px 0;\">\r\n   <li class=\"MsoListParagraph\">\r\n      <p style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">\r\n         <b>\r\n         <span style=\"font-size: 13px;color: black;\">Valuation of Indian Equities:</span> \r\n         </b>\r\n      </p>\r\n      <ul type=\"circle\">\r\n         <li class=\"MsoListParagraph\">\r\n            <span style=\"font-size: 13px;color: black;\">Indian equities are currently overvalued by approx 10%, with the Nifty 500 PE Ratio at 23.48.</span>\r\n         </li>\r\n         <li class=\"MsoListParagraph\">\r\n            <span style=\"font-size: 13px;color: black;\">Following the recent market correction, mid- and small-cap valuations have moderated to a certain extent.</span>\r\n         </li>\r\n      </ul>\r\n   </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul type=\"disc\" style=\"margin: 5px 0;\">\r\n   <li class=\"MsoListParagraph\">\r\n      <p style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">\r\n         <b>\r\n         <span style=\"font-size: 13px;color: black;\">India Outlook:</span> \r\n         </b>\r\n      </p>\r\n      <ul type=\"circle\">\r\n         <li class=\"MsoListParagraph\">\r\n            <span style=\"font-size: 13px;color: black;\">With the Union Budget 2026-27 announced on 1st February 2026, markets are navigating post-Budget volatility. The increase in Securities Transaction Tax (STT) on F&O trades has triggered profit booking and short-term uncertainty.</span>\r\n         </li>\r\n         <li class=\"MsoListParagraph\">\r\n            <span style=\"font-size: 13px;color: black;\">The government's continued focus on infrastructure, defence and manufacturing focused spending with fiscal discipline provides meaningful medium-term support, reinforcing India's position as a growth leader among emerging markets.</span>\r\n         </li>\r\n         <li class=\"MsoListParagraph\">\r\n            <span style=\"font-size: 13px;color: black;\">The India-EU trade agreement is a positive structural development, with benefits likely to materialize over the medium to long term.</span>\r\n         </li>\r\n      </ul>\r\n   </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div style=\"page-break-after: always;\"></div>\r\n<ul type=\"disc\" style=\"margin: 5px 0;\">\r\n   <li class=\"MsoListParagraph\">\r\n      <p style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">\r\n         <b>\r\n         <span style=\"font-size: 13px;color: black;\">Global Outlook:</span> \r\n         </b>\r\n      </p>\r\n      <ul type=\"circle\">\r\n         <li class=\"MsoListParagraph\">\r\n            <span style=\"font-size: 13px;color: black;\">United States: Continues to show resilience, supported by strong consumer spending and AI-led productivity gains. However, tariff regimes and debt sustainability remain key risks.</span>\r\n         </li>\r\n         <li class=\"MsoListParagraph\">\r\n            <span style=\"font-size: 13px;color: black;\">China: Growth remains steady, aided by exports and technology investments, despite lingering weakness in the property sector.</span>\r\n         </li>\r\n         <li class=\"MsoListParagraph\">\r\n            <span style=\"font-size: 13px;color: black;\">Europe & UK: Moderate expansion continues, with defence push and services-sector resilience offsetting consumer caution and trade-related pressures.</span>\r\n         </li>\r\n      </ul>\r\n   </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul type=\"disc\" style=\"margin: 5px 0;\">\r\n   <li class=\"MsoListParagraph\">\r\n      <p style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">\r\n         <b>\r\n         <span style=\"font-size: 13px;color: black;\">Equity Buying:</span> \r\n         </b>\r\n      </p>\r\n      <ul type=\"circle\">\r\n         <li class=\"MsoListParagraph\">\r\n            <span style=\"font-size: 13px;color: black;\">Large-cap equities are preferred due to relatively attractive valuations compared to mid- and small-caps.</span>\r\n         </li>\r\n         <li class=\"MsoListParagraph\">\r\n            <span style=\"font-size: 13px;color: black;\">To generate alpha, selective exposure to quality mid- and small-cap equities should remain part of the portfolio.</span>\r\n         </li>\r\n         <li class=\"MsoListParagraph\">\r\n            <span style=\"font-size: 13px;color: black;\">Investors already aligned with their strategic allocation may consider incremental investments during meaningful market corrections.</span>\r\n         </li>\r\n      </ul>\r\n   </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul type=\"disc\" style=\"margin: 5px 0;\">\r\n   <li class=\"MsoListParagraph\">\r\n      <p style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">\r\n         <b>\r\n         <span style=\"font-size: 13px;color: black;\">Gold & Silver:</span> \r\n         </b>\r\n      </p>\r\n      <ul type=\"circle\">\r\n         <li class=\"MsoListParagraph\">\r\n            <span style=\"font-size: 13px;color: black;\">At prevailing price levels, the margin of safety in silver is limited. Risk-reward dynamics appear skewed negatively for fresh long-term allocation.</span>\r\n         </li>\r\n         <li class=\"MsoListParagraph\">\r\n            <span style=\"font-size: 13px;color: black;\">Fresh allocations to pure silver are not suggested at current valuations.</span>\r\n         </li>\r\n         <li class=\"MsoListParagraph\">\r\n            <span style=\"font-size: 13px;color: black;\">Portfolio hedging should preferably be executed through staggered allocation to gold. We continue to have positive outlook on Gold.</span>\r\n         </li>\r\n      </ul>\r\n   </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul type=\"disc\" style=\"margin: 5px 0;\">\r\n   <li class=\"MsoListParagraph\">\r\n      <p style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">\r\n         <b>\r\n         <span style=\"font-size: 13px;color: black;\">Investor Guidance:</span>\r\n         </b>\r\n      </p>\r\n      <ul type=\"circle\">\r\n         <li class=\"MsoListParagraph\">\r\n            <span style=\"font-size: 13px;color: black;\">While we anticipate long-term growth, investors may experience short-term volatility.</span>\r\n         </li>\r\n         <li class=\"MsoListParagraph\">\r\n            <span style=\"font-size: 13px;color: black;\">We recommend investment in equities and commodities with a minimum time horizon of 5 to 7 years.</span>\r\n         </li>\r\n      </ul>\r\n   </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul type=\"disc\" style=\"margin: 5px 0;\">\r\n   <li class=\"MsoListParagraph\">\r\n      <b>\r\n      <span style=\"font-size: 13px;color: black;\">Portfolio Review Meeting: </span>\r\n      </b>\r\n      <span style=\"font-size: 13px;color: black;\">We would be happy to discuss your portfolio in detail. Please let us know your availability for a review meeting.</span>\r\n   </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>\r\n   <b>\r\n   <span style=\"font-size: 12px;color: black;\">Disclaimer: </span>\r\n   </b>\r\n   <span style=\"font-size: 12px;color: black;\">The perspectives provided reflect our expectations of the economy, market, and investments, which may or may not materialize. Investors are encouraged to conduct their own due diligence before investing.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 12px;\">The information contained herein is strictly confidential and meant solely for the use of the recipient only. This statement may not be changed or altered in any way in whole or in part so as to alter the purpose or intent of the statement. If you have received this statement by mistake or are not the intended recipient, please notify Alpha Capital immediately and destroy this statement.</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 12px;\">This statement is prepared at the specific request of the recipient and is meant for information purpose only and is not an official confirmation of any transactions mentioned in the statement. The statement is prepared on the basis of information received from the entity offering the product and Alpha Capital has not independently verified the said information. The information and the statements provided of the entities providing the respective products shall prevail and be final and binding over the information contained herein in this statement. The information contained in this statement are updated as and when received and updated from by the entity offering the products as a result of which there may be differences between the details contained herein and those reflected in the records of the respective entities. Alpha Capital is also not liable for delay in the receipt of this statement. For any clarification please feel free to get in touch with your Relationship Manager from Alpha Capital.</p>"
